Ibn \u2018Asakir reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever does not love knowledge, there is no good in him.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq 5\/408 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0639\u0633\u0627\u0643\u0631 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0627\u0641\u0639\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u0652 \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064f\u062d\u0650\u0628\u0651\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e \u0641\u0650\u064a\u0647\u0650 5\/408 \u062a\u0627\u0631\u064a\u062e \u062f\u0645\u0634\u0642 \u0644\u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0639\u0633\u0627\u0643\u0631","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27542,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/13\/best-answer-fool-silence\/","url_meta":{"origin":34348,"position":1},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Debate: Best answer to a fool is silence","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Imam al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah be pleased with him, said in his poetry, \u201cIf a fool speaks to you, do not answer him, for the best answer is silence. If you speak to him, you have delighted him. If you leave him, he nearly dies in anguish.\u201d Source: Di\u0304wa\u0304n al-Ima\u0304m al-Sha\u0304fi\u2019i\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26866,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/11\/17\/shafii-desire-no-praise\/","url_meta":{"origin":34348,"position":2},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Knowledge: I desire no praise or credit for teaching","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 17, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Hatim reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI never debated anyone and loved for him to be wrong. There is no knowledge in my heart but that I wish everyone could have it and attribute none of it to me.\u201d Source: A\u0304da\u0304b al-Sha\u0304fi\u2019i\u0304 wa Mana\u0304qibuh\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26012,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/04\/only-knowledge-benefit\/","url_meta":{"origin":34348,"position":3},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Knowledge: It is only knowledge if it benefits you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 4, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Rabia\u2019 reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cKnowledge is not merely what is memorized. Knowledge is what benefits.\u201d Source: al-Madkhal ila\u0301 al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 400 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0628\u064a\u0639 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0627\u0641\u0639\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0633\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u062d\u064f\u0641\u0650\u0638\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0646\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0639\u064e 400 \u00a0\u0627\u0644\u0645\u062f\u062e\u0644 \u0625\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0646\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0628\u0631\u0649 \u0644\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0647\u0642\u064a","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17324,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/27\/signs-hour-jahiliyyah-zina-khamr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34348,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sin: Signs of the Hour are ignorance, adultery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 27, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAmong the signs of the Hour are the reduction of knowledge, the prevalence\u00a0of ignorance, the prevalence of adultery, and the abundance of women and scarcity of men such that fifty women will be maintained by a single\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21512,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/07\/shafii-fiqh-imam-deen\/","url_meta":{"origin":34348,"position":5},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Fiqh: You must understand religion before leadership","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 7, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bayhaqi reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cYou must acquire understanding in the religion before assuming leadership. If you assume leadership first, there will be no way to acquire understanding.\u201d Source: al-Madkhal ila\u0304 al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 271 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\